# Wire Claude Code to the chassis (opt-in, reversible — unset to go back to direct Anthropic).
# 1. Boot the Anthropic frontend:  python -m local_offload.shim.run --anthropic --offload --profiles <your-profiles.json>
# 2. Point Claude Code at it:
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8088
#
# Notes:
#  - Trivial turns offload to your local backend with NO frontier key (proven by e2e-smoke.sh).
#  - Tool-bearing / multi-turn main turns pass THROUGH to Anthropic and need a real ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#    in your shell (subscription-OAuth Claude does not pass through a base-url override — use an API key).
#  - Start with WAVE_PROXY_OFFLOAD unset (passthrough + measure) and watch proxy.jsonl before enabling.
